<div class="ndx-walkthrough-prerequisites">
  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>

  <div class="govuk-warning-text">
    <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
    <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
      <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Important</span>
      You must have already requested the Simply Readable scenario via NDX:Try.
    </strong>
  </div>

  <p class="govuk-body">
    <a href="/scenarios/simply-readable/" class="govuk-link">Deploy the Simply Readable scenario</a> if you haven't already.
  </p>

  <div class="govuk-warning-text">
    <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
    <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
      <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Important</span>
      Deployment takes 5 to 10 minutes.
    </strong>
  </div>

  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-4">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">Why does deployment take this long?</span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      <p class="govuk-body">Simply Readable provisions a full serverless architecture:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li><strong>CloudFront distribution</strong> - global CDN for the web application (~3-5 min)</li>
        <li><strong>Cognito User Pool</strong> - authentication and user management</li>
        <li><strong>AppSync GraphQL API</strong> - real-time data synchronisation</li>
        <li><strong>Step Functions workflows</strong> - document translation and Easy Read pipelines</li>
        <li><strong>DynamoDB tables</strong> - job tracking and metadata</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
        The wait is worth it - you get a fully functional document translation tool to evaluate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">You'll need</h3>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>Your CloudFormation stack to show <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--green">CREATE_COMPLETE</span></li>
    <li>The <strong>AppUrl</strong> from your stack's Outputs tab</li>
    <li>The <strong>AdminPasswordSecret</strong> link to retrieve your admin password from Secrets Manager</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">The story behind Simply Readable</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Simply Readable was built by <strong>Swindon Borough Council</strong> in partnership with AWS. The tool
  was co-created with <strong>Experts by Experience of a Learning Disability</strong> to ensure Easy Read
  output truly meets the needs of its users. It's now open source and adopted by councils across the UK
  and internationally, including Edinburgh, Newport, Southampton, and West Berkshire.
</p>

